[SN]TITLE[SN]
Charlton Athletic: Yoni Buyens joins on loan from Standard Liege

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Charlton Athletic have signed midfielder Yoni Buyens on a season-long loan from Belgian club Standard Liege.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 26-year-old, who has played more than 100 games in three seasons with Liege, is new manager Bob Peeters' first signing at The Valley.
Charlton also hope to complete a deal for FC Copenhagen's Igor Vetokele.
The clubs have agreed a fee for the striker, who is expected in London next week to discuss personal terms and undergo a medical.
